fes_chatbot_api/
│
├── app/
│   ├── api.py                  # Main FastAPI app with /chat and /stream endpoints
│   │
│   ├── core/
│   │   ├── config.py           # Loads environment variables, sets up OpenAI & Pinecone
│   │   └── logger.py           # Global logger setup for consistent logging
│   │
│   ├── models/
│   │   └── schema.py           # Pydantic schema for ChatRequest and response models
│   │
│   ├── services/
│   │   ├── openai_service.py   # Handles embeddings and GPT completions
│   │   ├── pinecone_service.py # Executes vector searches in Pinecone
│   │   └── rag_service.py      # Builds context and orchestrates the RAG workflow
│   │
│   ├── routers/
│   │   └── chat_router.py      # (Optional) Router for organizing chat endpoints
│   │
│   └── utils/
│       └── contact_utils.py    # Detects and handles contact or branch-related queries
│
├── .env                        # Environment variables (API keys, configs)
├── requirements.txt             # Python dependencies
├── main.py                      # Alternative entry point (if used instead of api.py)
└── README.md                    # Project documentation

From the root folder run this command to run it: 
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
